; FloorPickerOverlay — Sprint 22 S22-M2 (matchup_assignment fold).
; Hidden by default. Shown when player taps FloorButton; contains the
; per-biome floor selection grid that was previously the standalone
; matchup_assignment screen. Closed via Cancel (no change) or Select
